title: Daria Kasatkina’s Tumultuous and Triumphant Season
description: The tennis star has spoken out against Russia’s invasion of Ukraine and come out as gay with her partner, the figure skater and fellow Russian Natalia Zabiiako. And she’s winning.
dc:creator: Christopher Clarey
media:description: Daria Kasatkina will play Carolina Garcia on Saturday for a chance to advance to the semifinals at the WTA Finals.
